Before you Install Make sure you are on base with no desktop environment
To Install XFCE Run sudo pacman -S xfce4 xfce4-goodies lightdm lightdm-gtk-greeter; sudo systemctl enable lightdm; sudo systemctl start lightdm
Login To XFCE
Remove Plasma Meta With sudo pacman -Rns plasma-meta
Remove Kate sudo pacman -Rns kate
